A number of McAbs against the multi-epitope peptide were developed and only two McAbs showed immune reactivity to individually expressed peptides. Epitope S2 (KLRPFERDISNV), locating at 447–458 AA of spike protein, was specifically recognized by McAb D3D1 in Western blotting (Fig. 3B
) and ELISA (Fig. 4A
), and epitope S5 (PDPLKPTKRSF), locating at 789–799 AA of spike protein, was specifically recognized by McAb D3C5 in Western blotting (Fig. 3C) and ELISA (Fig. 4C).
